]}&#39;>;&lt;/div>;&lt;/aside>; &lt;/div>; &lt;p id=&quot;l8Tm5x&quot;>;花几分钟定制 Windows 通知以满足您的要求，您可以获得更平静、更少脱节的计算体验，同时仍然确保您不会错过任何重要警报.&lt;/p>; &lt;h2 id=&quot;GPbbo1&quot;>;应用通知&lt;/h2>; &lt;p id=&quot;WofnNK&quot;>;例如&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2022/3/17/22981999 /google-android-13-notification-opt-in-default-developer-preview&quot;>;Android&lt;/a>;、&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2022/6/6/23151443/ios -16-notification-features-apple-wwdc&quot;>;iOS&lt;/a>; 和 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/21284515/apple-macos-notifications-manage-alert-on-off-操作方法&quot;>;macOS&lt;/a>;，Windows 让您控制通知...&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/23819943/windows-pc-notification-control -change-how-to&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/23819943/windows-pc-notification-control-change-how-to" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/23819943/windows-pc-notification-control-change-how-to</id><author><name>大卫·尼尔德</name></author></entry><entry><published>2023-08-04T10:00:00-04:00</published><updated> 2023-08-04T10:00:00-04:00</updated><title>夏季追剧指南</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;《鬼屋鬼魂》中的静态照片。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/sRRldbPnkEWAf2-mxhhKpuTyfhY=/1x0:4500x2999/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/72513949/HOHH_105_Unit_01251R_1_2.0。 .jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;山屋闹鬼 |图片：Netflix&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p>;我们精心挑选了 10 部剧集，这些剧集要么已经完成，要么前景光明。非常适合漫长炎热的夏夜。&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/23811117/best-shows-watch-binge-summer&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a >; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/23811117/best-shows-watch-binge-summer" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/23811117/best-shows-watch-binge-summer</id><author><name>陶里克·穆萨</name></author></entry><entry><published>2023-08-04T09:45:59-04:00</published><updated> 2023-08-04T09:45:59-04:00</updated><title> Coinbase 辩称其不交易证券，因此 SEC 的诉讼应被驳回</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;在青色、蓝色和黑色背景上带有圆形图案的 Coinbase 文字标记的插图。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/amU_nZZrAjTX7sD7unXAN5DpWd0=/0x0:3000x2000/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/72513877/acastro_STK019_02.0.jpg&quot;/>; &lt;figcaption>;插图由 Alex Castro / The Verge 提供&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;TrbxKo&quot;>;Coinbase 正在请求法官驳回美国证券交易委员会对其提起的诉讼。在&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.documentcloud.org/documents/23897368-sec-v-coinbase?responsive=1&amp;amp;title=1&quot;>;周五提交的动议&lt;/a>;中，Coinbase 坚称它不不得交易证券，从而使 SEC 的论点无效。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;1z4YLD&quot;>;&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2023/6/6/23750745/coinbase-sec-诉讼-未注册-证券-加密货币&quot;>;美国证券交易委员会 (SEC) 于 6 月起诉 Coinbase&lt;/a>;，指控该加密货币交易所作为未注册的经纪人、交易所和清算机构运营，违反了证券法。它还指控该公司通过其质押即服务计划出售未注册的证券，该计划通过参与区块链上的权益证明流程来奖励用户加密货币。&lt;/p>; &lt;div class=&quot;c- float-left c-float-hang&quot;>;&lt;div id=&quot;I0GlIm&quot;>; &lt;blockquote class=&quot;twitter-tweet&quot;>; &lt;p lang=&quot;en&quot; dir=&quot;ltr&quot;>;忽视该先例，美国证券交易委员会 (SEC) 违反了该先例正当程序，滥用自由裁量权，并放弃了自己先前对证券法的解释。作者...&lt;/p>; &lt;/blockquote>; &lt;/div>;&lt;/div>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2023/8/4/23819919/coinbase-securities- sec-lawsuit-dismissed&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2023/8/4/23819919/coinbase-securities-sec-lawsuit-dismissed" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2023/8/4/23819919/coinbase-securities-sec-lawsuit-dismissed</id><author><name>艾玛·罗斯</name></author></entry></feed>